data.meta_description:
577 likes, 24 comments - robynhitchcockofficial on March 3, 2024: "MELBOURNE! Cone you believe it? There are still some tickets left for my show this Friday March 8 at @thetotehotel . We sold out the Great Club in Sydney last Friday, and the two @merricreektavern gigs on Sunday March 10 are also sold out. So if you want to see me playing live in Australia this year, the Tote is the window thru which to waft. @daveyhellolane , Mick Thomas and @gusface_killah are the Aussie music legends joining me onstage. @heavyamber launch the show in a blizzard of 21st Century psychedelia. Doff your mind like a heavy hat, and let your balloon head float insideâ€¦(((ðŸŽˆ)))
Tickets in my bio and from The Tote itself. Photo by @emmaswiftsings . Promoter @pottsentertainment".
